{"tid":280324,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［父幹］香港間室內沙灘終於收左皮","createTime":"2017-06-12T04:03:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-03T08:24:08.000Z","uid":42097,"like":13,"dislike":161,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"31ed05c4f48e403b5a331fb87a97ca4cde278258","tid":280324,"uid":42097,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T04:03:30.000Z","msg":"頭先突然諗返起哥間hi野<br />\n上網search下原來汁左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n親愛的客户，<br />\n<br />\n多謝各位客戶對SandHouseHK 一直以來的愛載同支持！<br />\n我們一直致力為客人們提供娛樂，務求令客人們擁有開心既回憶。<br />\n由於公司業務擴展，室內沙灘將會遷移到內地，<br />\nSandHouseHK 的發展空間會更大及可以提供更多元化的玩樂設施給各位。<br />\n​<br />\n因此，SandHouseHK 的香港業務將於今日起暫停營業，在此對香港的客人作出深切的抱歉。<br />\n<br />\n我們再一次感謝一直以來支持SandHouseHK 的朋友仔。希望日後既日子可以再為你們服務。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n成功需父幹<br />\n香港衰左仲有錢返大陸開過一間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.sandhousehk.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.sandhousehk.com&d=z8Ld%2B2hpjPZmqBSST0GMlZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=3edf4cc6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.sandhousehk.com</a>"},{"pid":"8ae0bedb69f48463ca37e3c59f83c5f630a0de25","tid":280324,"uid":2959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T04:04:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c329d0f571c14c5c1d07bc449dac0bd240746c31","tid":280324,"uid":45185,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T04:05:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5999d7549a263c2ffe48b09d207dbdd5c38a3c4","tid":280324,"uid":30745,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T04:05:48.000Z","msg":"平心而論 佢idea幾好，因為可以比細路玩而家長/老師唔洗怕安全問題，或者好適合一啲要用到沙灘嘅場景佈置<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過最頂唔順係條撚屌話係靠自己點知最後比人知道係老豆科水比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79dfdd32934e5c5fb3d4bf3603bc5347814ec3af","tid":280324,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T04:05:50.000Z","msg":"一唔燈就收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22cfacd9fd46ad6bd561aa78a79559eb3fc67cf2","tid":280324,"uid":42097,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T04:06:07.000Z","msg":"我笑他人看不穿！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在三面環海的香港，戶外沙灘隨處可見，但竟然有人有勇氣在地少人多的地方搞室內沙灘。自上月某報章報導這個奇聞後，不少網民都紛紛議論，甚至有人批評它是「大型狗廁」、「不是沙灘是沙漠」。<a href=\"http://事隔一個月unwire.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E4%BA%8B%E9%9A%94%E4%B8%80%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88unwire.hk&d=z8Ld%2B2hpjPZmqBSST0GMlZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=c757b32f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">事隔一個月unwire.hk</a> 的依莉詩終於「排到隊」可以親身上訪問室內沙灘負責人 Peter。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/12/120545_af80802354a8b6840410c5e99af441be.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F12%2F120545_af80802354a8b6840410c5e99af441be.jpg&h=e1a1f67d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"69e7cd7aba71d063053af9161209972e410db20b","tid":280324,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T04:07:02.000Z","msg":"業務擴展<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab4fd7f6d41a050fb8f136f49f1817499970c51b","tid":280324,"uid":51121,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T04:09:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我笑他人看不穿！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在三面環海的香港，戶外沙灘隨處可見，但竟然有人有勇氣在地少人多的地方搞室內沙灘。自上月某報章報導這個奇聞後，不少網民都紛紛議論，甚至有人批評它是「大型狗廁」、「不是沙灘是沙漠」。<a href=\"http://事隔一個月unwire.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E4%BA%8B%E9%9A%94%E4%B8%80%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88unwire.hk&d=z8Ld%2B2hpjPZmqBSST0GMlZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=c757b32f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">事隔一個月unwire.hk</a> 的依莉詩終於「排到隊」可以親身上訪問室內沙灘負責人 Peter。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/12/120545_af80802354a8b6840410c5e99af441be.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F12%2F120545_af80802354a8b6840410c5e99af441be.jpg&h=e1a1f67d&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺係香港搵唔到合適既位開先係主因.<br />\n<br />\n要樓底高有自然光先得."},{"pid":"10e7a79d5e305bb2654f7afd090adcf3c4063694","tid":280324,"uid":42097,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T04:09:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/12/120906_b633e03475f3a48acaa68f1e1fc3a6a6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F12%2F120906_b633e03475f3a48acaa68f1e1fc3a6a6.jpg&h=529718ad&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/12/120908_7f2ec373064de02c66fbf81cc430d696.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F12%2F120908_7f2ec373064de02c66fbf81cc430d696.jpg&h=38d0ead9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無手足搵得返之前有張圖<br />\n影到個場成個狗廁咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31a727f2106e7a7a5a6cc240f0dbab78da03e31a","tid":280324,"uid":4210,"like":16,"dislike":3,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T04:11:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">汁你老母</span></span>"},{"pid":"5238aca3ff48915d33b32a86e38d0164d16830fd","tid":280324,"uid":42097,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T04:13:56.000Z","msg":"室內沙灘如大型狗廁？淡定回應<br />\n<br />\n終於都與 Peter 見面，我就一次過把網民的批評和自己的所見所聞都一一提出。對於網民及 <a href=\"http://unwire.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk&d=z8Ld%2B2hpjPZmqBSST0GMlZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=9e500d26\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">unwire.hk</a> 讀者們的批評，原來他一直都有觀察。被問到網民指室內沙灘是「大型狗廁」時，他表示當然不開心，不過每個人睇法都有所不同，就像 Apple 初初出 iPhone 的時候，也是沒有人看好，但現在也不是大買，所以他不會放棄。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好臭咩 ? 我習慣了，唔覺<br />\n<br />\n小編是中午來到的，可能是因為未有客人，網上相片中的充氣設施都沒有充氣，堆在沙上，整個沙灘就如廢墟一樣。而且如一位去過的朋友所說，小編一踏進去就已經嗅到一陣臭味。面對這個質問，Peter 坦言嗅不到味道，因為他長期在這裡，已經習慣了，並表示這種味道應該是剛剛消毒後的雙氧水味道，而小編覺得味道不好，是因為早了少少來到，到下晝客人來到的時候就會散，還有他們會加香精令味道像海灘一點。"},{"pid":"4f95276c54c7ea3fc9e7fef38e02c1b3dcf5cb55","tid":280324,"uid":42097,"like":4,"dislike":69,"score":-65,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T04:15:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">汁你老母</span></span></blockquote><br />\n得啦威啦正字特警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n( Show Blocked User - 關平 )"},{"pid":"02ebf196b91bda3a1ec880a0af3a6de7bf258fb9","tid":280324,"uid":39253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T04:15:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我笑他人看不穿！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在三面環海的香港，戶外沙灘隨處可見，但竟然有人有勇氣在地少人多的地方搞室內沙灘。自上月某報章報導這個奇聞後，不少網民都紛紛議論，甚至有人批評它是「大型狗廁」、「不是沙灘是沙漠」。<a href=\"http://事隔一個月unwire.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E4%BA%8B%E9%9A%94%E4%B8%80%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88unwire.hk&d=z8Ld%2B2hpjPZmqBSST0GMlZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=c757b32f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">事隔一個月unwire.hk</a> 的依莉詩終於「排到隊」可以親身上訪問室內沙灘負責人 Peter。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/12/120545_af80802354a8b6840410c5e99af441be.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F12%2F120545_af80802354a8b6840410c5e99af441be.jpg&h=e1a1f67d&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺係香港搵唔到合適既位開先係主因.<br />\n<br />\n要樓底高有自然光先得.</blockquote><br />\n香港根本唔岩開，沙灘周圍都係，去佢個室內沙灘仲要收錢"},{"pid":"ad8de1fb81d701c64b13f9597c7ddc06804940a2","tid":280324,"uid":51711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T04:16:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我笑他人看不穿！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在三面環海的香港，戶外沙灘隨處可見，但竟然有人有勇氣在地少人多的地方搞室內沙灘。自上月某報章報導這個奇聞後，不少網民都紛紛議論，甚至有人批評它是「大型狗廁」、「不是沙灘是沙漠」。<a href=\"http://事隔一個月unwire.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E4%BA%8B%E9%9A%94%E4%B8%80%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88unwire.hk&d=z8Ld%2B2hpjPZmqBSST0GMlZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=c757b32f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">事隔一個月unwire.hk</a> 的依莉詩終於「排到隊」可以親身上訪問室內沙灘負責人 Peter。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/12/120545_af80802354a8b6840410c5e99af441be.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F12%2F120545_af80802354a8b6840410c5e99af441be.jpg&h=e1a1f67d&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic