lyTime":"2017-06-12T04:28:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我笑他人看不穿！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在三面環海的香港，戶外沙灘隨處可見，但竟然有人有勇氣在地少人多的地方搞室內沙灘。自上月某報章報導這個奇聞後，不少網民都紛紛議論，甚至有人批評它是「大型狗廁」、「不是沙灘是沙漠」。事隔一個月<a href=\"http://unwire.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk&d=z8Ld%2B2hpjPZmqBSST0GMlZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=9e500d26\" target=\"_blank\">http://unwire.hk</a> 的依莉詩終於「排到隊」可以親身上訪問室內沙灘負責人 Peter。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/12/120545_af80802354a8b6840410c5e99af441be.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F12%2F120545_af80802354a8b6840410c5e99af441be.jpg&h=e1a1f67d&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺係香港搵唔到合適既位開先係主因.<br />\n<br />\n要樓底高有自然光先得.</blockquote><br />\n香港根本唔岩開，沙灘周圍都係，去佢個室內沙灘仲要收錢</blockquote><br />\n條友外國返黎以為香港去沙灘好麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d45d29e38990112ef2b11d05baaa82450abf126","tid":280324,"uid":26785,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T04:31:23.000Z","msg":"負皮比樓主嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bcfc6aba999d22a9132b68a4629195a78286430","tid":280324,"uid":1152,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T04:35:32.000Z","msg":"汁你老母"},{"pid":"dd48617f8559e12eb1da7061119e6bbb8d6bc8c6","tid":280324,"uid":44678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T04:35:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">汁你老母</span></span></blockquote><br />\n得啦威啦正字特警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n( Show Blocked User - 關平 )</blockquote><br />\n汁你老母啦</blockquote><br />\n而家打錯字都咁惡<br />\n痴線<